data.description: Nestled on a corner lot, this captivating POOL home, constructed with unmatched precision by Clarity Homes in 2018, offers both elegance and modern comfort. Immediately upon entering, you're greeted with a beautifully updated interior, showcasing 5 spacious bedrooms and 3 full, pristine bathrooms. An entertainer's dream, the home features a stunning, custom pool, beckoning guests and family for a refreshing dip or sun-soaked lounging. For those who love outdoor adventures or hobbies, the property boasts ample RV or boat parking. The private backyard, encased in tall 8ft fencing, serves as a serene oasis, perfect for afternoon relaxation or evening gatherings. Every detail of this home, from its inception to its meticulous maintenance, reflects the care it has received, making it not just a house but a cherished home awaiting its next fortunate owner.
